Input and Output: 

 

Input: 

    Input is a built-in function 

    Syntax: input(prompt) 

     Prompt ---->what message to be display on screen 

    Input function read the content from user in the form of string 

    The return type is string 

    To scan int /float/list/tuple---->explicit type cast 

 

Comments:- 

Single line comments # 

Multi line comment ---->string quotes '''     '''//" " "     """//'  ' 

